cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with completing partial shapes from shape acquisition setups. It could also belong to the Graphics (cs.GR) sub-category as it involves generating new shapes. The use of conditional generative modeling suggests that it could belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-category. Additionally, the paper involves learning a one-to-many mapping, which is a common problem in Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) sub-categories.
